Local template overrides
Files placed here will override templates from ../.template/
when generating workspaces with 'ow apply'.
Example: to customize odoorc for all your workspaces:
  cp workspaces/.template/odoorc.j2 workspaces/.template.overrides/odoorc.j2
  # then edit workspaces/.template.overrides/odoorc.j2 to your liking
This directory is gitignored - use it for personal customizations
that you don't want to track in the ow repository.
